  "Roy Chi Ping Chung cofounded Techtronic Industries with fellow billionaire Horst Julius Pudwill in 1985. ",
  "He debuted as a billionaire in 2021 as shares in Techtronic, a maker of power equipment and floor-care cleaning products, rose amid consumer demand. ",
  "The company makes cordless powered products for Milwaukee Industrial, Ryobi DIY power equipment and the iconic Hoover brand.",
  "He retired as group vice chairman and executive director of Techtronic in 2011, and has since been a non-executive director. "
